description:
Infrequent Uploads = Minecraft Movie. We finally have time to do some non-Ravager Rush stuff so it felt like a good time to deal with all my roof-rousers.

We head into town for some fun, shopping, and Doc poking. I end up on a surprise journey that nets me the Rocket Permit and marks me the #1 Poe Poe target. Our Shade-E antics return in the form of a new rocket shop.

Then we have some fun exploring and playing the mini-games on the server. I give an update on the changes I made to Ravager Rush after the 1st month. Cub's labyrinth almost takes me out IRL...

Hermitcraft Website: http://www.hermitcraft.com
